snippet.title: Tabletop Simulator "Serious" Trailer.
snippet.description:
Tabletop Simulator has launched on June 5, 2015:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/286160

Website:
http://www.berserk-games.com

Tabletop Simulator is the only simulator where you can let your aggression out by flipping the table! There are no rules to follow: just you, a physics sandbox, and your friends. Make your own games and play how YOU want!

Check out how there is much more to Tabletop Simulator than flipping tables!

To read more:
http://www.berserk-games.com/ts

Voice credit: Sean Beckett

Music: 
1st: Galactic Damages by Jingle Punks
2nd: Action Hero by Jingle Punks
